data.description: Seller is offering $1,000 carpet credit with an acceptable offer.  This affordable and spacious two-story home in the highly sought after Locust Ln cul-de-sac is back on market with no fault of the home or seller. The first floor of this home includes a large family and living room with hardwood flooring, propane gas fireplaces, and custom built-ins, an eat-in kitchen with plenty of storage space, laundry room, and sunroom which is perfect for enjoying these cool fall days! The second floor includes 3 bedrooms and the home's master suite with an attached en-suite. As a bonus, the master bedroom also includes a bonus room with hot tub, perfect for those cold winter days! Need even more space? This home also includes an additional 520+ finished square feet in the lower level, which would make the perfect home office, rec room, or home theatre.  Schedule your showings today, this home won't last long! Call Zach for 570 854 9034 for more information. Agents, please read the private remarks.
